usjuloebani Cemni ugulebelsyven ufalo, qalwulisagan Sobilo, da guli Cemi ganswmide, da taZar myav me uxrwnelisa xorcisa da sisxlisa Senisa, nu ganmagdeb me pirisa Senisagan, mxoloo romelsa gaqvs didi wyaloba.

